<plot>Set in a small Midlands town, Love Letters tells the story of Mary, a grieving widow whose past comes flying back into her life in a way she could never have expected. The only way for Mary to find a new path in life is by learning to let go, but it's difficult to let go when the things holding you back are the people you love.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?344714</url></doc>
